dc_title_s: North West Mounted Police Barracks -- Fort MacLeod -- UAV Photogrammetry -- 2016 (2 of 2)
dc_description_s: This data sets contains a 3D point cloud from UAV photogrammetry of the North West Mounted Police Barracks at Fort MacLeod and recorded for the purposes of assisting Alberta Cultural and Tourism with the preservation and conservation of the barracks.
dct_isPartOf_sm: North West Mounted Police Barracks -- Fort MacLeod -- UAV Photogrammetry -- 2016
